<div class="wizard_step">Account Creation</div>
<div class="wizard_instructions">
Thank you for joining us in the beta of the Roxiware web service for authors.  Not only will you help us 
shake any issues out of the web service, you'll be able to give valuable feedback on how we can improve
the service.<br/>
Let's get started.  First, lets set up an account.  You will use this account to manage your site.
</div>
<br/>
<br/>
<%= form_tag '/setup', :method=>"put", :authenticity_token=>false do -%>
  <%= label_tag "Email" %><%= email_field_tag :email, params[:email], { :autocomplete=>"off"}  %><br/><br/>
  <%= label_tag "Username" %><%= text_field_tag :username, nil, { :autocomplete=>"off"}  %><br/><br/>
  <%= label_tag "Password" %><%= password_field_tag :password, nil, { :autocomplete=>"off" }  %><br/>
  <%= label_tag "Password Confirmation" %><%= password_field_tag :password_confirmation, nil, { :autocomplete=>"off"} %><br/><br/>
  <%= hidden_field_tag :setup_type, "author" %>
  <%= hidden_field_tag :setup_step, "welcome" %>
  <%= button_tag "Create Account", :type=>"submit", :id=>"create_account" %>
<% end -%>
